Quote: Everybody loses in the end. That's why they call it the end.
Author: Leo Tindall

Quote: Depleted uranium is really fun. People should have more faith in it.
Author: Leo Tindall

Quote: May you always be a great programmer and a bad wizard
Author: Bruce Tindall

Quote: I'm not a bad man. I'm actually a very good man. I'm just a very bad wizard.
Author: L Frank Baum

Quote: You had me there, until the part where you were wrong.
Author: Leo Tindall

Quote: If you define everything as complex, nothing is simple.
Author: Sarah Schneewind
